<lb n="0507a04"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0507001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說十八臂陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0507a05"/>
<lb n="0507a06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0507002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西天譯經〕－【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0507002"><lem>西天譯經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經</rdg></app>三<note n="0507003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0507003"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">藏法師</rdg></app><note n="0507004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔朝散…臣〕十三字－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0507004" word-count="13"><lem>朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0507a07"/>明教大師臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0507a08"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時世尊告阿難言。世間眾生昧<note n="0507005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝于【明】</note><app n="0507005"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg></app>實智。輪
<lb n="0507a09"/>迴三界不知苦本。恣身口意造四重罪如是
<lb n="0507a10"/>之人深可憐愍。我有十八腎大陀羅尼。若有
<lb n="0507a11"/>眾生得此陀羅尼常持誦者。是人所作根本
<lb n="0507a12"/>罪業皆悉除滅。復能積集無量功德。爾時世
<lb n="0507a13"/>尊即說十八臂陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0507a14"/><p type="dharani">那謨阿彌多<note place="inline">引</note>婆<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;多<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>阿
<lb n="0507a15"/>囉曷<note place="inline">二合</note>帝三藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">三</note>那莫阿
<lb n="0507a16"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>阿&CB00085;路吉帝<note place="inline">引</note>說囉<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>&CB00155;地薩
<lb n="0507a17"/>埵<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">五</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>薩埵<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">六</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>嚕尼
<lb n="0507a18"/>迦<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">七</note>怛&CB00853;他<note place="inline">引八</note>唵三滿多伴捺哩<note place="inline">二合引九</note>三
<lb n="0507a19"/>滿多&CB00085;魯吉帝<note place="inline">引十</note>尾尸沙哥哩<note place="inline">引十一</note>尾塞怖
<lb n="0507a20"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>吒&CB00135;<note place="inline">引十二</note>度那播波尾多哩剛<note place="inline">二合引十三</note>摩摩
<lb n="0507a21"/>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵難左<note place="inline">十四</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">引</note>哩也
<lb n="0507a22"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路吉帝<note place="inline">引</note>說囉<note place="inline">十五</note>&CB00085;羅末&CB00619;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;羅末
<lb n="0507a23"/>&CB00619;<note place="inline">引十六</note>塞怖<note place="inline">引二合</note>吒&CB00135;塞怖<note place="inline">二合引</note>吒&CB00135;<note place="inline">十七</note>達髻
<lb n="0507a24"/>達髻<note place="inline">十八</note>嗢度&CB00135;哥<note place="inline">引</note>謨髻枳<note place="inline">引十九</note>&CB00085;尸哥囉尼
<lb n="0507a25"/><note place="inline">引二十</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訥瑟吒<note place="inline">二合引</note>那<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;哩惹<note place="inline">二合</note>野
<lb n="0507a26"/><note place="inline">二十一</note>尾&CB00085;哩惹<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">二十二</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訥瑟&CB02824;
<lb n="0507a27"/><note place="inline">二合引二十三</note>&CB00085;設摩<note place="inline">引</note>那野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引二十四</note>曷羅曷
<lb n="0507a28"/>羅<note place="inline">二十五</note>左羅左羅<note place="inline">二十六</note>&CB00425;左&CB00425;左<note place="inline">二十七</note>&CB00085;尸<note place="inline">引</note>酤
<lb n="0507a29"/>嚕<note place="inline">二十八</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>部<note place="inline">引</note>多<note place="inline">引</note>難&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1118.0507b" n="0507b"/>
<lb n="0507b01"/>賀<note place="inline">引二十九</note></p>
<lb n="0507b02"/><p>爾時阿難聞佛世尊說此陀羅尼經已。歡喜
<lb n="0507b03"/>信受作禮而退</p>
